  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Oxidative stress has been reported to play a role in melasma pathophysiology. The objective
      of the study is to compare oral superoxide dismutase (GLISODin) to placebo, in combination to
      sunscreen to decrease melasma severity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
